entries.femaleVariant: User! I have an important message for you!
All right. Hit me.
Anything.
Hit me with it.
Anything.
While running a routine diagnostic check, I discovered a file with my owner's metadata.
Name. Regina Jones.
OK. I'll take you to Regina.
No. I'm keeping you.
OK. I'll take you to Regina.
Don't think so... You're mine now. Finders keepers.
You are the best user I know!
Increasing volume by 300 percent. TAKE ME BACK TO MY OWNER!!!
The name "Skippy" mean anything to you?
Hey, the name "Skippy" ring any bells? Fits in a holster, more than a little psycho...
You have Skip?! Little bastard got swiped a while back... Let me see him!
Let's see how you're doin'. Run diagnostics.
[Hand over Skippy]
There a reward?
Performance – 82 percent. Memory – damaged. Mode – Puppy-Loving Pacifist. Permanent lock.
Permanent lock? Hm. Something's gonked... Return to factory settings.
Please set pistol name.
Performance – 82 percent. Memory – damaged. Mode – Stone Cold Killer.
Hmm... I'd better do a full scan. At least it still works.
You killed him...
Where'd you get him from?
Wait... Where'd you get this iron anyway?
Eh... Knew a guy, everyone called him Danish... Great techie. I mean, before he started hitting the bottle.
Anyway, poker game... Danish cleaned out his credchip, then bet his gun. I think you can put together the rest.
The combat features are great... But why the voice interface, you know? Weird as hell.
So – somethin' for my trouble?
You... You killed him! You killed Skippy.
Sure... Here you go.
Come on. He's just an algorithm. Not a shred of consciousness.
Not so sure. He... he had a personality. Quirks, mannerisms.
Mhm. Protocol errors. A good, hard reset always helps.
Say anything to continue.
Automated response. Ha ha ha! The joke gets funnier the more you say it!
It looks like you're trying to be funny. Automated response. Ha ha ha! I have never heard that one before!
User. Please return me to my real owner. Thank you in advance.
Yell all you want.
Bad user! Bad user!
Choom, I'm the only user you know. Your memory got wiped.
Fun fact. There is a 92 percent probability Regina Jones will reward you!
Feels kinda weird now. It's too... quiet.
Hm. Maybe you should get a dog.
Maybe. Someday. See ya, Reggie.
Hmmm... Daisy.
My name is Daisy.
